ma Rousseff|Rousseff]])</small>\n! 21.32%<br><small>([[Marina Silva|Silva]])</small>\n! 0.61%<br><small>([[Eduardo Jorge|Jorge]])</small>\n! 33.55%<br><small>([[A\u00e9cio Neves|Neves]])</small>\n! 0.75%<br><small>([[Everaldo Pereira|Pereira]])</small>\n! 0.64%\n! ''9.64%''\n|-\n| [http://g1.globo.com/politica/eleicoes/2014/noticia/2014/10/datafolha-votos-validos-dilma-tem-44-aecio-26-e-marina-24.html Datafolha]\n| 3\u20134 October 2014\n| 18,116\n| 1%<br><small>(Genro)</small>\n| style=\"background:#FFE3E3\" |'''40%<br><small>(Rousseff)</small>'''\n| 22%<br><small>(Silva)</small>\n| 1%<br><small>(Jorge)</small>\n| '''24%<br><small>(Neves)</small>'''\n| 1%<br><small>(Pereira)</small>\n| 2%\n| ''9%''\n|-\n| [https://www1.folha.uol.com.br/poder/2014/09/1525042-datafolha-mostra-acirramento-da-disputa-entre-aecio-e-marina-pelo-segundo-lugar.shtml Datafolha]\n| 29\u201330 September 2014\n| 7,520\n| 1%<br><small>(Genro)</small>\n| style=\"background:#FFE3E3\" |'''40%<br><small>(Rousseff)</small>'''\n| '''25%<br><small>(Silva)</small>'''\n| <1%<br><small>(Jorge)</small>\n| 20%<br><small>(Neves)</small>\n| 1%<br><small>(Pereira)</small>\n| <1%\n| ''10%''\n|-\n| [https://politica.estadao.com.br/noticias/eleicoes,no-ibope-dilma-abre-14-pontos-de-marina-que-perde-folga-em-relacao-a-aecio,1568705 Ibope]\n| 27\u201329 September 2014\n| 3,010\n| 1%<br><small>(Genro)</small>\n| style=\"background:#FFE3E3\" |'''39%<br><small>(Rousseff)</small>'''\n| '''25%<br><small>(Silva)</small>'''\n| <1%<br><small>(Jorge)</small>\n| 19%<br><small>(Neves)</small>\n| 1%<br><small>(Pereira)</small>\n| <1%\n| ''14%''\n|-\n| [http://g1.globo.com/politica/eleicoes/2014/noticia/2014/09/dilma-tem-38-marina-29-e-aecio-19-aponta-pesquisa-ibope.html Ibope]\n| 20\u201322 September 2014\n| 3,010\n| <1%<br><small>(Genro)</small>\n| style=\"background:#FFE3E3\" |'''38%<br><small>(Rousseff)</small>'''\n| '''29%<br><small>(Silva)</small>'''\n| <1%<br><small>(Jorge)</small>\n| 19%<br><small>(Neves)</small>\n| 1%